ace="Verdana" style="font-size: 8pt;"><img align="middle" height="22" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20051203015934im_/http://www.ptv.com.vn/images/guide/age/item_mix_09.gif" width="22" /></font></td>\r\n							</tr>\r\n						</tbody>\r\n					</table>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table bgcolor="#6f9bce" border="0" cellpadding="4" id="table22">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5d461">\r\n					&nbsp;</td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">: Kh&ocirc;ng thể thất bại</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#b9d9a4">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">: C&oacute; khả năng thất bại, mất sheltoms, tiền v&agrave; cấp độ age của item sẽ bị trừ đi 1 hoặc 2 level.</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#88acc0">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">&nbsp;</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">: C&oacute; khả năng thất bại, mất sheltoms, tiền, item v&agrave; cấp độ age của item sẽ bị trừ đi 1 hoặc 2 level.</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><img border="0" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20051203015934im_/http://www.ptv.com.vn/images/guide/age/Aging_IMG_01.jpg" vspace="10" /><br />\r\n	Nếu bạn đặt item v&agrave;o trong cửa sổ Aging<br />\r\n	&nbsp;bạn c&oacute; thể thấy y&ecirc;u cầu cần bao nhi&ecirc;u tiền v&agrave; bao nhi&ecirc;u sheltoms</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><img border="0" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20051203015934im_/http://www.ptv.com.vn/images/guide/age/Aging_IMG_02.jpg" vspace="10" /><br />\r\n	Một khi bạn Aging th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng, bạn sẽ thấy<br />\r\n	một thanh trắng v&agrave; d&ograve;ng aging mức độ &quot;+0&quot; tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin về item.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Item Maturation<br />\r\n	Một khi bạn đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng việc Aging, bạn sẽ thấy một thanh trắng tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin của item. Khi thanh trắng n&agrave;y đầy (từ tr&aacute;i qua phải), bạn sẽ được cộng th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c khả năng v&agrave;o item, được gọi l&agrave; &quot;Item Maturation&quot;. Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch n&oacute; l&agrave;m việc:</span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table bgcolor="#6f9bce" border="0" cellpadding="5" id="table23">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Những item chuy&ecirc;n về tấn c&ocirc;ng<br />\r\n					(Axes, Maces, Wands/Staves)</span></span></td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Bạn đ&aacute;nh b&igrave;nh thường</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Những item dựa v&agrave;o critical<br />\r\n					(Claws, Bows, Scythes, Swords, Javelins)</span></span></td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Đ&aacute;nh một đ&ograve;n critical</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Những item chuy&ecirc;n về chống đỡ<br />\r\n					(Armors, Robes, Orbs/Beads)</span></span></td>\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">L&atilde;nh đ&ograve;n tấn c&ocirc;ng của qu&aacute;i vật</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n				<td>\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Những item chuy&ecirc;n về chống đỡ<br />\r\n					(Shields)</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Đỡ được một đ&ograve;n tấn c&ocirc;ng của qu&aacute;i vật</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Ghi ch&uacute;: Y&ecirc;u cầu level của bạn l&agrave; +/- 10 so với level của qu&aacute;i vật để aging bar c&oacute; thể tăng l&ecirc;n</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Sau khi qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh &quot;Item Maturation&quot; ho&agrave;n tất th&igrave; việc aging item đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng v&agrave; n&oacute; sẽ thể hiện mức level ở tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh item. Level y&ecirc;u cầu cơ bản để sử dụng item sẽ tăng l&ecirc;n 1 level mỗi 2 cấp Aging. Bạn h&atilde;y cố gắng l&ecirc;n level trước khi ho&agrave;n tất việc aging một item.</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">C&aacute;c chỉ số nhận được khi item được Aging:</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">[C&aacute;c vũ kh&iacute; tấn c&ocirc;ng]</span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="1" id="table24">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#6f9bce">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Chủng loại</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#6f9bce">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Hiệu ứng c&ocirc;ng th&ecirc;m cho mỗi Aging Level</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Axes</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+10 Attack Rating</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Claws</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+0.5 Critical, +5 Attack Rating</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Maces</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+10 Attack Rating</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Wands &amp; Staves</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum attack Power,<br />\r\n					+10 Attack Rating, +10&nbsp;MP</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Scythes</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+0.5 Critical, +5 Attack Rating</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Bows</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+0.5 Critical</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Swords</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+0.5 Critical, +5 Attack Rating</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Javelins</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+1 Minimum Attack Power, +1 Maximum Attack Power,<br />\r\n					+0.5 Critical</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">[C&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng cụ chống đỡ]</span></span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<table border="0" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="1" id="table25">\r\n		<tbody>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#6f9bce">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Chủng loại</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#6f9bce">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Hiệu ứng c&ocirc;ng th&ecirc;m cho mỗi Aging Level</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Shields</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+0.5 Block, +0.2 Absorb</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Orbs &amp; Beads</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+10% Defense, +0.5 Absorb</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#d5e4f3">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">Armors &amp; Robes</span></span></td>\r\n				<td bgcolor="#e8e8e8">\r\n					<span style="font-family:tahoma,geneva,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size:14px;">+5% Defense, +0.5 Absorb</span></span></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		</tbody>\r\n	</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '1', 0);
